# Raw schemas dumped by SchemaService.test.ts for developer-eye inspection.
#
# These files are *inputs* to the `aggressivelySimplify` snapshot tests: each
# `raw-<preset>.json` is the byte-for-byte schema produced by the analyzer
# from the deterministic generator (seed = 42) before simplification kicks in.
#
# They're regenerated on every `vitest` run, can be tens of MB for the larger
# presets, and aren't required to reproduce test results (the seed gives us
# determinism).  Keep them local — the corresponding `simplified-*.json`
# snapshots one level up are the committed source of truth.
raw/

